  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38df1097&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fb0DPsa8Pwiaeo7sm2vP2Yics777PwhNGdT9uBtGIpxBBia2KgsLAG8myCdZnQHBcZ4s74KA4bEatnlhWknEShoiapvYmk0IYc1T1dgLfsybicrro%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>感谢大家的支持</p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">5 万只“阶跃龙虾”，抢空了<img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"128\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 20px;vertical-align: middle;background-size: cover;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b7ac87b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FShocked.png\">……</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">StepClaw&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上线这几天，我们的后台留言爆了，不少人都来问如何部署、还有很多朋友自发分享使用感受：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/b0DPsa8PwiafibHsUKTNlEavvt3G9zibBCIq6D89gU8a6bGnsictXZuicCIzXhqpskAHCaYG2EgC0cKba4YoibhwmGupM38XI9WsSGO1NgDgwHoVs/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1641.9999999999998\" data-cropy2=\"531.2352941176471\" data-imgfileid=\"100003689\" data-ratio=\"0.32265625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:578px;height:187px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8963008e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Fb0DPsa8PwiafQJDCibUqkYMiab0OCmH8qAyRp9wPSSEpibibbqAs348CYEWGXFpwmDoHicnolFOJN4LIkkf6KzdW6EDbP5Iibic9oyzxahKqiagKG9Go%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们感受</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">到了</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;StepClaw</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;的火热</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，更感</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">受到了大家</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的支持与喜爱</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">！</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3 月 12 日下午两点，我们在阶跃AI 上线了 StepClaw 云端一键部署，开放了 5 万个免费云养虾名额。没想到大家的领养热情远超我们预期，现已全部抢空。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了回馈大家，我们决定再追加 20000 个免费名额，同样的配置：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">5000 万 Step 3.5 Flash Tokens、云服务器、存储全包；免费一个月，先到先得。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一键部署功能同步恢复，打开阶跃AI APP 即可体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b0DPsa8Pwiacpo9AX9GMRicqmEicjfa98qe3w8L8vSic2dHJDTwz9WiarX1cKXXcacvYewuxy6lyZBe09GvxeDRdQ2icE1qUdbyR2ZkZsVuLUoyUo/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"771\" data-imgfileid=\"100003692\" data-ratio=\"1.6666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9b2bd096&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fb0DPsa8Pwiacpo9AX9GMRicqmEicjfa98qe3w8L8vSic2dHJDTwz9WiarX1cKXXcacvYewuxy6lyZBe09GvxeDRdQ2icE1qUdbyR2ZkZsVuLUoyUo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">上一波没抢到的朋友们，这次别再错过<img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"128\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 20px;vertical-align: middle;background-size: cover;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40c48d71&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FLetMeSee.png\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">24 小时在线、能记事、会搜索、懂你心意</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的赛博助手，等你来领。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如何获取<img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"128\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 20px;vertical-align: middle;background-size: cover;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7f1de71&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2FExpression%2FExpression_78%402x.png\">：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前往网页版「阶跃AI」：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://www.stepfun.com/chats/new\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.stepfun.com/chats/new</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前往应用商店下载「阶跃AI」APP：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 245px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100003682\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7de186fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fb0DPsa8PwiaficerTInNJPLTe3eRK9xwaN5tNpnvfX1ibFojwHqrXqaXvyUgHbUz9VKazRluLwwsJGfdsaUYzJt4oeYqTeGRcJiaZ5HfIHJsnNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阶跃星辰宣布其 AI 助手 StepClaw 云端部署名额遭抢购，并决定追加 2 万个包含免费 Token 和服务器资源的体验名额。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阶跃星辰宣布其 AI 助手 StepClaw 云端部署名额遭抢购，并决定追加 2 万个包含免费 Token 和服务器资源的体验名额。",
  "summary": "本文是阶跃星辰官方发布的一则产品动态公告。文章指出其推出的 StepClaw（昵称“阶跃龙虾”）云端一键部署功能上线后反响热烈，首批 5 万个免费名额已迅速发放完毕。为了回馈用户，官方宣布追加 2 万个免费名额，每个名额包含 5000 万 Step 3.5 Flash Tokens 以及为期一个月的免费云服务器和存储资源。文章旨在引导用户通过阶跃 AI 的网页版或 APP 领取资源并体验其具备记事、搜索功能的赛博助手产品。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "StepClaw 云端部署名额供不应求，首批 5 万个名额已售罄。",
      "explanation": "文章强调了产品的市场热度，通过“抢空”和“后台爆了”等描述展示用户对 StepClaw 部署的高度关注。"
    },
    {
      "point": "官方追加 2 万个免费体验名额，提供高额资源补贴。",
      "explanation": "追加名额包含 5000 万 Token 及一个月免费服务器资源，旨在降低用户使用门槛，吸引更多人尝试其 AI 助手。"
    },
    {
      "point": "StepClaw 定位为全天候在线、具备记忆与搜索能力的赛博助手。",
      "explanation": "简要勾勒了产品核心功能，强调其在记事、信息检索及情感理解方面的应用价值。"
    }
  ],
